1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:07,920
Más sakin* ijkuak ijkon yonochiu,

2
00:00:07,920 --> 00:00:08,720
José,

3
00:00:08,720 --> 00:00:10,600
on yejuan chanej* Arimatea,

4
00:00:10,600 --> 00:00:15,780
okitlajtlanilij Pilato permiso para kiktis itlalnakayo Jesús.

5
00:00:15,780 --> 00:00:19,480
José san ichtaka* inomachtijkau katka Jesús,

6
00:00:19,480 --> 00:00:22,060
pampa kinmakasiya on hebreos*.

7
00:00:22,060 --> 00:00:23,940
Pilato okauilij,

8
00:00:23,940 --> 00:00:28,020
niman José oyaj niman okitkik itlalnakayo Jesús.

9
00:00:28,020 --> 00:00:29,940
No ijki Nicodemo,

10
00:00:29,940 --> 00:00:34,200
on yejuan achtoj oyajka okinotsato Jesús ijkuak tlayoua,

11
00:00:34,200 --> 00:00:43,880
oajsik niman kuajkiya kanaj treinta kilos ajuiyalistli tlachijchijtli ikan mirra niman iyayo sen xojtli itoka áloe.

12
00:00:43,880 --> 00:00:45,160
Ijkon tej,

13
00:00:45,160 --> 00:00:49,240
José niman Nicodemo okiktikej itlalnakayo Jesús,

14
00:00:49,240 --> 00:00:58,580
niman okitetejkuixkej ikan sen tela fina itoka lienzo yejuan okitlalilijkej se tlaneloltipan ajuiyalistli.

15
00:00:58,580 --> 00:01:03,920
Okichijkej ken kichiuaj on hebreos* ijkuak kintokaj on mikatsistimej.

16
00:01:03,920 --> 00:01:06,880
Ne kampa okajkopilojkej Jesús,

17
00:01:06,880 --> 00:01:09,660
onkatka sen kojtlakijloj.

18
00:01:09,660 --> 00:01:17,300
Niman ipan on kojtlakijloj onkatka sen yenkuik tlalkontli ijtik sen teostotl kampa xe yakaj kitôkayaj.

19
00:01:17,300 --> 00:01:22,700
Ompa okitlalijkej itlalnakayo Jesús pampa on tlalkontli nisiu onkatka,

20
00:01:22,700 --> 00:01:28,240
niman pampa ye peuaya on tonajli sábado.

21
00:01:28,240 --> 00:01:33,200
Saniman ipan on tonajli domingo ijkuak sanken*  tlayouatok katka,

22
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:36,720
María Magdalena oyaj itech on tlalkontli.

23
00:01:36,720 --> 00:01:38,480
Niman ijkuak oajsik,

24
00:01:38,480 --> 00:01:44,680
okitak ika xok ompa onkatka on tetl yejuan kitentsakutikatka on tlalkontli.

25
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:51,280
Kemaj onotlaloj ne kampa nemiyaj Simón Pedro niman on nomachtijketl yejuan Jesús sanoyej* kitlajsojtlaya*,

26
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:53,120
niman okinmijlij:

27
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:59,680
—Yokejkuanijkej toTEKO ipan itlalkon niman xtikmatij kanon okauatoj.

28
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:05,440
Kemaj Pedro niman on okse nomachtijketl okiskej niman oyajkej itech on tlalkontli.

29
00:02:05,440 --> 00:02:08,020
On omemej onotlajtlalojkej,

30
00:02:08,020 --> 00:02:15,440
pero on okse más sanoyej onotlaloj xken Pedro niman achtopa yejua oajsik itech on tlalkontli.

31
00:02:15,440 --> 00:02:21,800
Onopachoj para ontlachix ijtik on tlalkontli niman san okitak ompa onkaj on telas istakkej,

32
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:23,920
pero xokalakito.

33
00:02:23,920 --> 00:02:29,480
Kemaj Simón Pedro oajsik ikuitlapan niman okalakito ijtik on tlalkontli.

34
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:32,980
Yejua no okitak ompa onkaj on telas istakkej.

35
00:02:32,980 --> 00:02:37,920
Niman no okitak on tela yejuan ika okuatejkuixkaj Jesús.

36
00:02:37,920 --> 00:02:43,560
On tela yejuan ika okuatejkuixkaj xsan sekan onkatka iuan on telas istakej,

37
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:47,520
yej tepayolijtikatka niman oksekan onkatka.

38
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:52,720
Kemaj no okalakito on okse nomachtijketl yejuan achtopa oajsik.

39
00:02:52,720 --> 00:02:55,560
Ijkuak kuajli okitak tlinon yonochiu,

40
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:58,360
okineltokak ika Jesús nemi.

41
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,640
Yejuamej tej,

42
00:02:59,640 --> 00:03:08,740
sanken* xe kajsikamatiyaj on Yektlajkuilojli yejuan kijtoua ika Jesús ika onkatka yoliuis* niman nokuiteuas ipan itlalkon.

43
00:03:08,740 --> 00:03:12,880
Kemaj yejuamej on nomachtijkej* oyajkej para inchan.

44
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:17,220
Pero María onokau ikiauak on tlalkontli niman chokaya.

45
00:03:17,220 --> 00:03:22,160
Chika chokatikatka onopachoj para ontlachix ijtik on tlakontli,

46
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:26,760
niman okintak omemej ángeles ikan intlaken istak.

47
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:32,040
Yejuamej yejyeuatikatkaj ne kampa onkatka on itlalnakayo Jesús.

48
00:03:32,040 --> 00:03:36,320
Se yeuatikatka kampa itsontlan niman okse ikxitlan ika.

49
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:39,400
Niman on ángeles okitlajtoltijkej:

50
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:40,760
—Siuatl,

51
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:42,520
¿tline* tichoka?

52
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:43,940
Yejua okinmijlij:

53
00:03:43,940 --> 00:03:49,120
—Pampa yokejkuanijkej noTEKO niman xnikmati kanon okauatoj.

54
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:51,780
Kemaj ijkuak ijkon okijtoj,

55
00:03:51,780 --> 00:03:56,100
onomalakachoj niman okitak Jesús ika ompa ijkatikatka,

56
00:03:56,100 --> 00:03:59,000
pero xkimatiya ika yejua Jesús.

57
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:01,180
Kemaj Jesús okitlajtoltij:

58
00:04:01,180 --> 00:04:02,400
—Siuatl,

59
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:04,280
¿tline tichokatikaj?

60
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:06,800
¿Akinon tiktejtemoua?

61
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:09,680
Yejua kinemiliaya ika on akin okinots,

62
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:13,080
on yejuan kijtlapiya on kojtlakijloj.

63
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,920
Yejua ika okijlij:

64
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:15,880
—Señor,

65
00:04:15,880 --> 00:04:17,760
tla tejua otikuikak,

66
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:21,920
xnechijli kanon otikauato para nejua nikonanas.

67
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:24,280
Kemaj Jesús okijlij:

68
00:04:24,280 --> 00:04:26,000
—¡María!

69
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:28,280
Yejua onomalakachojtikis,

70
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:31,120
niman okijlij ikan tlajtojli hebreo:

71
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:33,240
—¡Raboni!

72
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:36,800
—yejuan kijtosneki “Temachtijketl”.

73
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:38,680
Jesús okijlij:

74
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:42,520
—Maka xnechkiktsi pampa xe niau itech noTajtsin.

75
00:04:42,520 --> 00:04:48,860
Pero xuiya niman xkimijliti nokniuan ika yeniau itech noTajtsin niman nemoTajtsin,

76
00:04:48,860 --> 00:04:51,760
itech noDios niman nemoDios.

77
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:58,700
Kemaj María Magdalena oyaj okinmachistito on nomachtijkej* ika yejua yokitak inTEKO,

78
00:04:58,700 --> 00:05:02,700
niman ika yejua okijlij in tlajtlamach*.

